                  </persName>
            . I took him in charge as the prosecutor brought him along the Old Bailey.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A boy, eight or ten years old, took the handkerchief - I tapped the gentleman on the shoulder, and told him of it; he immediately knocked me through a pane of glass, and gave me a black eye - then he followed the boy, and took it from him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18230910-121-person1241">
                  JOSEPH 
                  FOURDRINIER
               <interp inst="t18230910-121-person1241" type="surname" value="FOURDRINIER"></interp>
