                     <interp inst="t18230910-121-person1241" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . He stated this at the Mansion House; but never told me a boy had taken it. Nobody touched me on the shoulder.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 16.</p>
